summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1885, for the improvement of West Lander Street, from 36th Avenue Southwest to California Avenue, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues all in the City of Seattle by constructing concrete sidewalks under Ordinance No. 19553 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
